## Phase 7 — Challenger Map (Optional)
**Goal:** Beat the 45-turn reference record on [01_the_impossible_dream.txt](file:///home/smoustaj/goinfre/fly-in/maps/challenger/01_the_impossible_dream.txt) (25 drones).

### 7.1 Advanced techniques
- Full **Conflict-Based Search (CBS)** implementation
- **Iterative deepening** on turn count
- **Simulated annealing** or **genetic algorithm** for schedule optimization
- Profile and optimize hot paths (avoid re-computation)

### 7.2 Memory & performance analysis
- Document algorithm complexity
- Profile memory usage with large drone counts
- Benchmark against all map tiers

